Overwrites the python version in the given conda env dictionary.

{
    "name": "env",
    "channels": [...],
    "dependencies": [
        ...,
        "python=3.10.*",  <- Overwrite this
    ],
}

Overwrites the pip dependencies section in the given conda env dictionary.

{
    "name": "env",
    "channels": [...],
    "dependencies": [
        ...,
        "pip",
        {"pip": [...]},  <- Overwrite this
    ],
}
